        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Simplify the sum: $(3x^2 - 4x + 8) + (2x^2 + 7x - 5)$.",
        "options": [
          "$5x^2 + 3x + 3$",
          "$5x^2 + 11x + 13$",
          "$5x^4 + 3x^2 + 3$",
          "$6x^2 + 3x + 3$"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Combine like terms: $(3x^2 + 2x^2) + (-4x + 7x) + (8 - 5) = 5x^2 + 3x + 3$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Perform the subtraction: $(5x^3 - 2x^2 + 4) - (x^3 + 6x^2 - 7)$.",
