        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Distribute the negative sign: $5x^3 - x^3 - 2x^2 - 6x^2 + 4 + 7 = 4x^3 - 8x^2 + 11$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the product: $3x^2(4x^3 - 5x + 2)$.",
