        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Multiply the coefficients and add the exponents: $3 \\cdot 4(x^{2+3}) - 3 \\cdot 5(x^{2+1}) + 3 \\cdot 2(x^2) = 12x^5 - 15x^3 + 6x^2$."
